        "text": "To observe and understand how the economic system actually operates â€” through continuous, data-driven analysis tested against real outcomes â€” so that only theories that match observed results survive, and those that fail are discarded. The ultimate objective is to maintain a live, self-correcting understanding of where the system stands now and where it is likely to move next â€” enabling proactive positioning to profit from structural changes while remaining de-risked from surprises.",
